article.headline: LeDee scores 21 as San Diego State rolls past Fresno State 74-47
article.description: — Jaedon LeDee scored 21 points and San Diego State cruised to a 74-47 victory over Fresno State in a Mountain West Conference opener on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: LeDee scores 21 as San Diego State rolls past Fresno State 74-47
article.story: SAN DIEGO -- — Jaedon LeDee scored 21 points and San Diego State cruised to a 74-47 victory over Fresno State in a Mountain West Conference opener on Wednesday night. LeDee made 9 of 12 shots and 3 of 4 free throws for the Aztecs (12-2), who have won five in a row. Micah Parrish and Lamont Butler both scored 11 with Parrish adding seven rebounds and Butler four assists. Xavier DuSell led the Bulldogs (7-7) with 10 points. ------ Get poll alerts and updates on AP Top 25 basketball throughout the season.
